      <p>Protocols marked <strong>Partial</strong> in the table above allow certain configuration options — for example, adjusting the sensitivity threshold for the Prayer Recovery Protocol's distress detection, or customizing the language used in the Grace-First Matching interface. These configurations must remain within the bounds defined in the Lightek Partner Configuration Guide.</p>
      <p>To request a configuration change for a partial protocol, submit a <a onclick="window.open('lightek-support.html','_blank')">Compliance support ticket →</a> with the specific protocol, the change requested, and the business justification. Configuration changes are reviewed by the Lightek compliance team within 48 hours.</p>
